#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int t;
	cin>>t;
    int h1,m1,s1,h2,m2,s2,d;
    while(t--)
    {
        cin>>h1>>m1>>s1;
        cin>>h2>>m2>>s2;;
        d=(h2-h1)*3600+(m2-m1)*60+(s2-s1);
        d=d%400;
        if((d>=0 && d<=99)||(d>=200 && d<=299))
            printf("S\n");
        else
            printf("C\n");
    }
    return 0;
}
